<% content_for(:title, "Memorial Funds — Christopher Quentin") %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-title text-stone-800 mb-2">Bees &mdash; Waste &mdash; Water &mdash; Music</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-blue-800 mb-6">Christopher&rsquo;s Works</p>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
    <p>Join us in continuing Christopher&rsquo;s impact!</p>
    <p>
      Christopher gave so much in his 36 years and by supporting this fund your contribution will
      provide the potential for continued impact in his memory.
    </p>
    <p>
      The McMullen Family will thoughtfully determine grantees based on initiatives that keep
      Christopher&rsquo;s passions alive, and grant amounts will be considered in the context of total
      fund value. Reports of grant recipients will be shared on the Christopher Memorial website.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have projects that need support (starting a beehive, planting a tree, hosting a concert
      etc.,) please don&rsquo;t hesitate to get in touch.
    </p>
    <p>You can also contribute to specific projects below.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-title text-blue-900 mb-2">Bees</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600">Supporting beekeeping projects and pollinator conservation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-title text-blue-900 mb-2">Water</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600">Water-related environmental initiatives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-title text-blue-900 mb-2">Zero Waste</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600">Waste reduction and sustainability efforts.</p>
      <%= link_to "Learn more →", zero_waste_path, class: "text-blue-800 hover:text-blue-700 text-sm mt-2 inline-block" %>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-title text-blue-900 mb-2">Dartmouth Conducting Endowment</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-stone-600">
        <p>
          Christopher (aka &lsquo;Zeke&rsquo;) spent formative years at Dartmouth. He flourished,
          pursuing his passions as a music major and Senior Fellow, as a member of the Chamber Singers
          and Handel Society, and through a term abroad studying music.
        </p>
        <p>
          He was also a Presidential Scholar, a German language drill instructor, and a member of
          the Outing Club.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now, on the anniversary of his passing, we wish to honor Zeke and his time at Dartmouth by
          memorializing him through a gift that will strengthen the College.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <p>
          <a href="https://securelb.imodules.com/s/1353/events/events.aspx?sid=1353&gid=431&pgid=15529&cid=38949&bledit=1&dids=508&appealcode=campaignws" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-800 hover:text-blue-700 underline">Donate by credit card or PayPal</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://dartgo.org/wiretransfer" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-800 hover:text-blue-700 underline">Wire transfer</a>
          &mdash; Enter &ldquo;Christopher McMullen-Laird Memorial Fund&rdquo; in Gift Allocation box.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-500">
          By check: Payable to &ldquo;Trustees of Dartmouth College&rdquo;, directed to:
          Gift Recording Office, 6066 Development Office, Hanover, NH 03755-4400.
          Reference &ldquo;Christopher McMullen-Laird Memorial Fund&rdquo;.
          Toll free: 1-800-490-7010.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
